---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy | Save Editor Online"
  description="Cookie Policy for Save Editor Online. Learn how we use cookies."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> December 6, 2025
      </p>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files that are stored on your computer or mobile device when you
          visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and to
          provide information to the owners of the site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies for the following purposes:</p>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto mt-6">
          <table
            class="min-w-full bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg"
          >
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700">
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"
                  >Category</th
                >
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"
                  >Purpose</th
                >
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"
                  >Examples</th
                >
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700">
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Essential</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
                  >Necessary for the website to function (e.g., language preferences).</td
                >
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
                  ><code>lang</code>, <code>theme</code></td
                >
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Analytics</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
                  >To understand how visitors interact with our website.</td
                >
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
                  ><code>_ga</code>, <code>_gid</code> (Google Analytics)</td
                >
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Advertising</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
                  >To display personalized advertisements based on browsing habits.</td
                >
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300"
                  ><code>__gads</code> (Google AdSense)</td
                >
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          You can control and/or delete cookies as you wish. You can delete all cookies that are
          already on your computer and you can set most browsers to prevent them from being placed.
          If you do this, however, you may have to manually adjust some preferences every time you
          visit a site and some services and functionalities may not work.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          To learn more about how to manage cookies, visit <a
            href="https://www.aboutcookies.org/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">aboutcookies.org</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          In addition to our own cookies, we may also use various third-parties cookies to report
          usage statistics of the Service, deliver advertisements on and through the Service, and so
          on.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about our Cookie Policy, please contact us at:
          <a href="mailto:privacy@saveeditor.top" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline"
            >privacy@saveeditor.top</a
          >
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "name": "Cookie Policy",
      "url": "https://saveeditor.top/cookie-policy",
      "description": "Cookie Policy for Save Editor Online. Learn how we use cookies.",
      "lastReviewed": "2025-12-06",
      "specialty": "LegalDocument"
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
